Key.Original: The Zodiac Hurricane H733 IO RIB is part of the Hurricane range of RIBS that are mission specific and are used by the most discriminating operators who demand the utmost in ruggedness and reliability. All Hurricane models have removable collars for ease of maintenance as well as the capability of interchanging with Durarib foam collars.
